  "detailed_description": "<h1>WISHLIST NOW</h1><p><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2200230/extras/558645267493f0c42368fcc3d3716858.poster.avif?t=1745254866\" width=600 height=82 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2200230/extras/558645267493f0c42368fcc3d3716858.webm?t=1745254866\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2200230/extras/558645267493f0c42368fcc3d3716858.mp4?t=1745254866\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2200230/extras/94f51de130479f1b128141fec8ab686b.poster.avif?t=1745254866\" width=600 height=144 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2200230/extras/94f51de130479f1b128141fec8ab686b.webm?t=1745254866\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2200230/extras/94f51de130479f1b128141fec8ab686b.mp4?t=1745254866\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>CursedSword is a Sokoban-style sliding puzzle game where your attacks grow stronger with every move! Bash through monsters, traps, and obstacles to crack snappy puzzles, battle bosses in turn-based showdowns, discover hidden treasures, and unlock game-changing power-ups. Join the hero on a quest to break the curse and bring justice to his hometown!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2200230/extras/d20664ff5d7e09aeeefde1e87e865fa8.poster.avif?t=1745254866\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2200230/extras/d20664ff5d7e09aeeefde1e87e865fa8.webm?t=1745254866\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2200230/extras/d20664ff5d7e09aeeefde1e87e865fa8.mp4?t=1745254866\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Unlock power-ups on your journey to the Countess Castle. Stuck on a tricky puzzle? These are your secret weapon. Use them strategically to overcome obstacles and break through when you're stuck.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2200230/extras/032043d90dfe6ccdcb8698b573cd7900.poster.avif?t=1745254866\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2200230/extras/032043d90dfe6ccdcb8698b573cd7900.webm?t=1745254866\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2200230/extras/032043d90dfe6ccdcb8698b573cd7900.mp4?t=1745254866\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Face challenging turn-based boss battles and test your skills against the Countess's fiercest champions.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2200230/extras/48a928df360e0bf71a201b83f872db7f.poster.avif?t=1745254866\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2200230/extras/48a928df360e0bf71a201b83f872db7f.webm?t=1745254866\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2200230/extras/48a928df360e0bf71a201b83f872db7f.mp4?t=1745254866\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features</h2></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Embark on a journey through a spooky island ruled by danger and evil monsters.<br></li><li>Hundreds of deadly puzzles.<br></li><li>Retro inspired 2D top-down pixel graphics.<br></li><li>A snappy grid-based movement that lets you plan every move!<br></li><li>Eight mysterious areas of the Haunted Island full of monsters and traps!<br></li><li>Challenging turn-based boss fights protecting the way to the Countess's Castle.</li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2200230/extras/94f51de130479f1b128141fec8ab686b.poster.avif?t=1745254866\" width=600 height=144 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2200230/extras/94f51de130479f1b128141fec8ab686b.webm?t=1745254866\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2200230/extras/94f51de130479f1b128141fec8ab686b.mp4?t=1745254866\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>CursedSword is a Sokoban-style sliding puzzle game where your attacks grow stronger with every move! Bash through monsters, traps, and obstacles to crack snappy puzzles, battle bosses in turn-based showdowns, discover hidden treasures, and unlock game-changing power-ups. Join the hero on a quest to break the curse and bring justice to his hometown!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2200230/extras/d20664ff5d7e09aeeefde1e87e865fa8.poster.avif?t=1745254866\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2200230/extras/d20664ff5d7e09aeeefde1e87e865fa8.webm?t=1745254866\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2200230/extras/d20664ff5d7e09aeeefde1e87e865fa8.mp4?t=1745254866\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Unlock power-ups on your journey to the Countess Castle. Stuck on a tricky puzzle? These are your secret weapon. Use them strategically to overcome obstacles and break through when you're stuck.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2200230/extras/032043d90dfe6ccdcb8698b573cd7900.poster.avif?t=1745254866\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2200230/extras/032043d90dfe6ccdcb8698b573cd7900.webm?t=1745254866\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2200230/extras/032043d90dfe6ccdcb8698b573cd7900.mp4?t=1745254866\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Face challenging turn-based boss battles and test your skills against the Countess's fiercest champions.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2200230/extras/48a928df360e0bf71a201b83f872db7f.poster.avif?t=1745254866\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2200230/extras/48a928df360e0bf71a201b83f872db7f.webm?t=1745254866\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2200230/extras/48a928df360e0bf71a201b83f872db7f.mp4?t=1745254866\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features</h2></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Embark on a journey through a spooky island ruled by danger and evil monsters.<br></li><li>Hundreds of deadly puzzles.<br></li><li>Retro inspired 2D top-down pixel graphics.<br></li><li>A snappy grid-based movement that lets you plan every move!<br></li><li>Eight mysterious areas of the Haunted Island full of monsters and traps!<br></li><li>Challenging turn-based boss fights protecting the way to the Countess's Castle.</li></ul>",
